      • extractMessageContentFromNotify

        public static Object extractMessageContentFromNotify(org.oasis_open.docs.wsn.b_2.NotificationMessageHolderType notifyHolderType)
        Extract the Message element from a WS-Notification NotificationMessageHolderType wrapper This method is an overloaded counterpart of the Notify version, that assumes that the invoking method is iterating over holderTypes in a Notify. The job of this method is then to extract the content of the current holderType.
        Parameters:
        notifyHolderType - The wrapper to extract the message content from
        Returns:
        The message object contained within the notificationmessageholdertype

      • interpretTerminationTime

        public static long interpretTerminationTime(String time)
                                     throws org.oasis_open.docs.wsn.bw_2.UnacceptableTerminationTimeFault
        Takes a termination-time string, represented either as XsdDuration or XsdDatetime, and returns it specified (end)date.
        Parameters:
        time - The termination-time string: either XsdDuration or XsdDatetime.
        Returns:
        The parsed termination time as a timestamp, long.
        Throws:
        org.oasis_open.docs.wsn.bw_2.UnacceptableTerminationTimeFault - If the passed in String was not a valid XsdDuration or XsdDatetime time, or if some RuntimeException occurred during the extraction. This can be caused by the DatatypeConverter which is used to parse XsdDatetime.
